Body:
assert Chord.Chord('C', [(1, 0), (3, 4), (5, 7)], '').get_spelling() == ['C',
    'E', 'G']
assert Chord.Chord('C', [(1, 0), (3, 3), (5, 7)], '').get_spelling() == ['C',
    'Eb', 'G']
assert Chord.Chord('C', [(1, 0), (3, 3), (5, 6)], '').get_spelling() == ['C',
    'Eb', 'Gb']
assert Chord.Chord('C', [(1, 0), (2, 3), (5, 5)], '').get_spelling() == ['C',
    'D#', 'Gbb']
assert Chord.Chord('C', [(1, 0), (3, 4), (5, 7), (9, 14)], '').get_spelling(
    ) == ['C', 'E', 'G', 'D']
assert Chord.Chord('C#', [(1, 0), (3, 3), (5, 6), (7, 9)], '').get_spelling(
    ) == ['C#', 'E', 'G', 'Bb']
assert Chord.Chord('C', [(1, 0), (3, 3), (7, 9), (9, 13)], '').get_spelling(
    ) == ['C', 'Eb', 'Bbb', 'Db']
assert Chord.Chord('Cb', [(1, 0), (3, 4), (5, 7)], '').get_spelling() == ['Cb',
    'Eb', 'Gb']
